{"tid":405240,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，想報下年Top-up/ UGC想問少少野","createTime":"2017-09-18T16:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T14:11:01.000Z","uid":89032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad1a744639884052b589189e9555598c4091d83","tid":405240,"uid":89032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"今年原本有個speed offer 最後reject左去左做長工<br />\n想話做一年當gap year順便儲工作經驗同填左啲工作時數之後辭工再讀返書<br />\n<br />\n聽另一位同我同CC同公司但唔同位嘅巴打話早知做我呢個位<br />\n佢話如果係我個位做一年野可以入返CITY CS<br />\n但我想問工作經驗係有助報non jupas嘅咩？<br />\n個工作係very related to the course<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而GPA方面我同佢一樣都係 2.79，唔同嘅係佢eng而我係近cs多啲嘅programme<br />\n<br />\n其實我都知呢個分入UGC基本係無可能<br />\n但都想問下最後嘅希望 polyU<br />\n<a href=\"http://www51.polyu.edu.hk/eprospectus/ug/non-jupas-adhd-grad/2017/61431-sy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww51.polyu.edu.hk%2Feprospectus%2Fug%2Fnon-jupas-adhd-grad%2F2017%2F61431-sy&d=wca9uF3WYcW0QzuqSMqPTcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5e78888a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www51.polyu.edu.hk/eprospectus/ug/non-jupas-adhd-grad/2017/61431-sy</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www51.polyu.edu.hk/eprospectus/ug/non-jupas-adhd-grad/2017/61434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww51.polyu.edu.hk%2Feprospectus%2Fug%2Fnon-jupas-adhd-grad%2F2017%2F61434&d=wca9uF3WYcW0QzuqSMqPTcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=006f8352\" target=\"_blank\">http://www51.polyu.edu.hk/eprospectus/ug/non-jupas-adhd-grad/2017/61434</a><br />\n呢兩科有冇機會收2.79?<br />\n如果加埋呢年工作經驗呢？<br />\n<br />\n另外上年比嘅Offer係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個月佢過左交留位費deadline仲想挽留我讀，但我已經入左職。所以無諗住去讀，比自己感受下工作辛勞先。<br />\nPT degree其實都有考慮過，而家返5日FT都覺得少左好多私人時間，得六日可以打下機約下人食飯，訓都訓唔好，所以應該handle唔到PT degree。<br />\n<br />\n如果有經驗嘅巴絲可以答一答我我會十分感激。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過點都好，後路都會係去返Top up。我都知夢一早發完，要讀U我應該一早就要發奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13162c73b03581d13b5949e86b2539c6f8b69918","tid":405240,"uid":89032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年原本有個speed offer 最後reject左去左做長工<br />\n想話做一年當gap year順便儲工作經驗同填左啲工作時數之後辭工再讀返書<br />\n<br />\n聽另一位同我同CC同公司但唔同位嘅巴打話早知做我呢個位<br />\n佢話如果係我個位做一年野可以入返CITY CS<br />\n但我想問工作經驗係有助報non jupas嘅咩？<br />\n個工作係very related to the course<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而GPA方面我同佢一樣都係 2.79，唔同嘅係佢eng而我係近cs多啲嘅programme<br />\n<br />\n其實我都知呢個分入UGC基本係無可能<br />\n但都想問下最後嘅希望 polyU<br />\n<a href=\"http://www51.polyu.edu.hk/eprospectus/ug/non-jupas-adhd-grad/2017/61431-sy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww51.polyu.edu.hk%2Feprospectus%2Fug%2Fnon-jupas-adhd-grad%2F2017%2F61431-sy&d=wca9uF3WYcW0QzuqSMqPTcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5e78888a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www51.polyu.edu.hk/eprospectus/ug/non-jupas-adhd-grad/2017/61431-sy</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www51.polyu.edu.hk/eprospectus/ug/non-jupas-adhd-grad/2017/61434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww51.polyu.edu.hk%2Feprospectus%2Fug%2Fnon-jupas-adhd-grad%2F2017%2F61434&d=wca9uF3WYcW0QzuqSMqPTcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=006f8352\" target=\"_blank\">http://www51.polyu.edu.hk/eprospectus/ug/non-jupas-adhd-grad/2017/61434</a><br />\n呢兩科有冇機會收2.79?<br />\n如果加埋呢年工作經驗呢？<br />\n<br />\n另外上年比嘅Offer係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個月佢過左交留位費deadline仲想挽留我讀，但我已經入左職。所以無諗住去讀，比自己感受下工作辛勞先。<br />\nPT degree其實都有考慮過，而家返5日FT都覺得少左好多私人時間，得六日可以打下機約下人食飯，訓都訓唔好，所以應該handle唔到PT degree。<br />\n<br />\n如果有經驗嘅巴絲可以答一答我我會十分感激。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過點都好，後路都會係去返Top up。我都知夢一早發完，要讀U我應該一早就要發奮<img src=\"/as